criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adult kidney transplant recipients who underwent transplantation at Zaporizhzhia
             Transplant Center;

          -  cadaveric or living single kidney only transplant;

          -  informed written consent;

          -  adequate intraoperative biopsy (in total ≥ 7 glomeruli and ≥ 1 arteries in preimplant
             and postreperfusion biopsies);

          -  complete follow-up data up to 5 years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  not consent with research;

          -  non-complete follow-up data up to 5 years.
